{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "c3d4e5f6-a7b8-9012-cdef-123456789012",
    "name": "Foundation API - Complete Workflow",
    "description": "Complete test suite for Foundation Pillar\n\nBased on: specs/foundation/foundation.pillar.v2.yml\n\nCovers:\n- Reference data (age bands, smoker profiles, geo states)\n- Address management\n- Benefit catalog (catalogs, items, levels)\n- Discount programs\n- Guidelines (documents, versions, acceptance)\n- KYC verification\n\nWorkflow order:\n1. Seed reference data (age-bands, smoker-profiles, geo-states)\n2. Add address to an owner\n3. Create benefit catalog → add items → add levels\n4. Create discount program → deactivate\n5. Create guideline document → create version → publish → accept\n6. Create KYC record → verify or reject\n\nAll endpoints require: foundation:admin (except Guideline.Accept)\nAll mutating endpoints require: Idempotency-Key header",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
